<emphasis id="B337EC959EABABF03D04B1F85D5F80E2" bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="111">Holotype</emphasis>
, ♀ [NEFU; on card], China, Sichuan Province, Guangyuan City, Qingchuan County, 21 VIII 2015, leg. Ye Chen and Chao Zhang, by sweeping. 
<emphasis id="8DE1AC4B07F42B1A89B53F4C0CF44A00" bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="111">Paratypes</emphasis>
